# landing.e2.agency — Landing Page & Offers Platform

A dedicated Astro 5 project for building high-converting landing pages for e2 Agency. Deployed to `landing.e2.agency` via Cloudflare Pages. Each landing page/offer gets its own route, built with reusable CRO-optimized components.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Supabase Cost**: Your e2.agency org is on a **paid plan** — a new project will cost **$10/month**. For just landing page lead capture, we have two options:
> 1. **Reuse an existing project** (e.g. add a `landing_leads` table to AgencyOS or another project) — **$0 extra**
> 2. **Create a new dedicated project** — **$10/month**
>
> Which do you prefer? For now I'll plan around option 1 (reuse existing) since you mentioned wanting a free plan.

> [!NOTE]
> **Formflow Integration**: We'll embed Formflow (`getformflow.io`) via iframe/script embed for all lead capture forms. This means Supabase may not even be needed initially if Formflow handles all form submissions.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Framework | **Astro 5** (SSG, zero-JS by default) |
| Interactive | **React** (via `@astrojs/react` islands) |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS v4** |
| Animations | **GSAP + ScrollTrigger** |
| Forms | **Formflow** (getformflow.io embed) |
| Backend | **Supabase** (optional, for analytics/leads) |
| Deployment | **Cloudflare Pages** |
| Domain | `landing.e2.agency` |

## Proposed Changes

### Project Scaffold

#### [NEW] `C:\Users\Admin\.gemini\antigravity\scratch\e2-landing\`

Astro 5 project initialized with:
- `@astrojs/react` — React island components
- `@astrojs/tailwind` or Tailwind v4 native — styling
- `gsap` — animations
- Configured for static output (SSG) for Cloudflare Pages

### Project Structure

```
e2-landing/
├── src/
│   ├── layouts/
│   │   └── BaseLayout.astro        # HTML shell, fonts, meta, GSAP init
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── Hero.astro              # Above-the-fold hero with headline + CTA
│   │   ├── SocialProof.astro       # Logos, testimonials, stats
│   │   ├── Services.astro          # What e2 offers
│   │   ├── CTA.astro               # Formflow embed + call-to-action
│   │   └── Footer.astro            # Minimal footer
│   ├── islands/
│   │   └── FormflowEmbed.tsx       # React component for Formflow embed
│   └── pages/
│       └── index.astro             # First landing page
├── public/
│   └── fonts/                      # Self-hosted premium fonts
├── astro.config.mjs
├── tailwind.config.ts
├── package.json
└── tsconfig.json
```

### First Landing Page (index.astro)

The initial landing page for e2 Agency — a high-converting agency offer page with:
- **Hero**: Bold headline, subtext, gradient background, animated CTA button
- **Social Proof**: Client logos, revenue stats, testimonial cards
- **Services**: What e2 does (email marketing, retention, CRO)
- **CTA Section**: Formflow embed for booking a call / getting an audit
- **Footer**: Minimal with links

## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run build` — Astro static build succeeds with zero errors
- Lighthouse CLI audit targeting 95+ performance score

### Manual
- Open dev server in browser, verify all sections render correctly
- Verify Formflow embed loads and is interactive
- Test mobile responsiveness at 375px, 768px, 1024px breakpoints
- Verify GSAP scroll animations trigger correctly
- User deploys to Cloudflare Pages and confirms `landing.e2.agency` resolves
